AI-Powered PPTX Presentation Generator
Groq + SerpAPI + Unsplash + python-pptx + Tkinter

This project automatically generates complete, professional PowerPoint presentations using Groq’s LLM, real-time image fetching (SerpAPI + Unsplash), and python-pptx slide rendering.
A simple Tkinter GUI makes it easy for anyone to create PPTs instantly.

Features
1. AI-Generated Slide Content

Uses Groq LLM (llama-3.3-70b-versatile)

Produces expert-level bullet points

No childish or unprofessional tone

Structured and business-ready content

2. Automatic Image Insertion

Fetches relevant images via SerpAPI (Google Images)

Falls back to Unsplash if needed

Auto-scales images

Always positions image on the right

Ensures no overlap with text

3. Clean Slide Design

Uses theme0.pptx as base template

Title slide always correct

Final “Thank You” slide is auto-added

Removes duplicated slide titles

Adjusted text width for readability

4. Tkinter GUI for Easy Use

Enter topic, number of slides, model, and API key

Click one button → PPT is generated in seconds


